# Netscape HTTP Cookie File
# Export from a throwaway YouTube account (e.g. the "Get cookies.txt LOCALLY"
# browser extension) and save as secrets/cookies.txt (gitignored).
# Only needed if the deploy host's IP gets bot-checked by YouTube.
#
# Format (tab-separated):
# .youtube.com	TRUE	/	TRUE	0	COOKIE_NAME	cookie_value
